snippet.title: Hermetika VR Gameplay (19 02 2020)
snippet.description:
A fast, yet casual and vertical (!) endless runner in VR? Spin, crouch, jump!
In HermetikaVR your are a deity sent from the clouds to save the Hermetikos and their infinite tower. Climb up, use your pocket portal to send them up to safety, secure the tower and… don't get caught up by the sea!
